🔥 Core OIDC flow
!! ------------------------------ !!
Client registration
Authorization Code Flow
Login (authentication)
Consent
Authorization code issuance
Token exchange
ID Token (JWT)

----- : What /authorize must do : -----
Your server must:
Validate client
Validate redirect_uri
Ensure user is logged in
Generate authorization code
Redirect back to client

workin of authorization :

1. Chat App → /authorize
2. OIDC Server validates client
3. User already logged in
4. SHOW consent page
5. User clicks Allow
6. Server generates auth code
7. Redirect back to chat app

👉 “Authorization Server (mini version)”

It includes:

client registration (client_id, client_secret)
/authorize endpoint
login system (user authentication)
consent screen
authorization code generation
(next) token exchange endpoint

